{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_01","textHome":"我从第一次来神滨的时候就感觉有些……违和。@乍一看，好像和我们住的见泷原没什么区别，@但空气中的魔力波动，和见泷原的完全不同。@不早不晚，就是那个时候感觉到的……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_18","textHome":"我最喜欢的魔法……应该是做红茶的魔法吧。@战斗结束之后，能够休息一下就好了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_19","textHome":"感觉自己跨越了界限。我还能更强吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_20","textHome":"我看到了……在我心中广阔的景色……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_21","textHome":"虽然我在成为魔法少女的时候，@没心思考虑活下去以外的愿望。@但如果有机会的话，@我又会怎么做呢……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":100}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_22","textHome":"过去我一直都是一个人在战斗。@作为魔法少女的烦恼辛苦还有害怕，@没法和任何人坦白，一直独自一人……@但是，现在我有了同伴……@所以我能够坚持下去……这是毋庸置疑的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_23","textHome":"和同伴一起战斗的时候特别安心、幸福。@这是一个人战斗的时候所感受不到的。@有和自己心意相通的人存在，@真是一件非常幸运的事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_24","textHome":"啊，来了来了。这样就全员到齐了。@那么，就出发吧！前往夏天的大海！@嗯哼，期待得不由自主就激动起来了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_25","textHome":"早上好。昨晚睡得好吗？@睡眠不足的话，到大海里可就危险了哦。@虽然兴奋得睡不着也是能理解的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":300}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_26","textHome":"我买来了西瓜。@吃完午饭之后，一起去砍西瓜吧。@我特意准备的超大西瓜哦。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":100}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_27","textHome":"太阳快下山了……@海上的落日虽然很美，但也有种寂寞的感觉。@特别是在开心过后，就格外……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.1,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":300}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_03","textHome":"看起来是麻烦的对手呢……小心为上……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_28","textHome":"说到夏夜那就是，烟花！@嗯，比起试胆大会还是烟花更好！@我并不是在害怕哦？@只是，黑暗的地方很危险对吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":400}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_29","textHome":"嗯嗯。海风很舒服吧。@玩累了之后，在阴凉处听着风的声音，@不觉得很美好吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_30","textHome":"哎呀，好像是巡逻的时间了。@到了夏天也不能掉以轻心。@那么，出发吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":0}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.1,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_31","textHome":"虽说天气很热，但战斗也不能不像样。@特别是和我们的复制品战斗的时候，@可不能行动笨拙。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_32","textHome":"因为是夏天，就穿着泳装来怎么样？@虽然想这么说，但指挥别人是不好的吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":200550,"motion":300}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_33","textHome":"我还是第一次用沙子造这么大一个城堡呢。@说起来，多亏了晓美同学一直在帮我。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.4,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_34","textHome":"说起来，暑假作业做得怎么样了？@玩得太开心，结果忘记写作业可是不行的哦。@每天都认真对待才行！因为这是很重要的事。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_35","textHome":"要玩沙滩抢旗吗？@没问题，不过我可不会输的哦！@那么，在此之前得好好做准备活动才行。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.5,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":1}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_36","textHome":"虽然也想吃柠檬味的，@不过最后我还是试着点了红茶味的刨冰。@红茶味的刨冰很少见吧。@啊呜。嗯嗯嗯嗯～好吃。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_37","textHome":"虽然实用性和流行的设计……@是挑选泳装的基础，不过机会难得，@我就挑了自己中意的一件。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_04","textHome":"没问题……@我怎么会让可爱的后辈受伤呢……！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_30":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_38","textHome":"晓美同学的泳装，很不错吧？@她本人好像担心穿比基尼会不会太过惹眼，@我倒是觉得她应该再拿出点自信来比较好。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100}]}],"group_31":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_39","textHome":"鹿目同学的泳装成熟中透着可爱，真棒呀。@这么适合她的泳装，@一定是很了解她的人为她选的吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":7.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_32":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_40","textHome":"从我成为魔法少女之后，@就没有想到我还能和不用彼此介意的朋友一起玩耍。@这段时间对我来说真是相当宝贵。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.7,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200550,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100}]}],"group_33":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_50_41","textHome":"啊，抱歉。刚刚在发呆……@我想起了过去，在我成为魔法少女之前，@我和家人一起来到海边时的回忆……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.9,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200550,"motion":300}]}],"group_34":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_42","textHome":"别担心，我怎么会输呢。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_35":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_43","textHome":"工作完成了呢。"}]}],"group_36":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_44","textHome":"呼……真可惜。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550}]}],"group_37":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_45","textHome":"接下来，去喝杯茶吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550}]}],"group_38":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_46","textHome":"大家，来我家坐坐吧？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.3,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_39":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_63","textHome":"我来了结你！最终射击！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_4":[{"autoTurnFirst":0.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_05","textHome":"算是解决了一件事吧。@鹿目同学她们在身边真是帮大忙了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":400}]}],"group_40":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_64","textHome":"久等了……请收下这一击！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_41":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_65","textHome":"抱歉……我要迅速收拾掉你们了。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_42":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_66","textHome":"就这样……一口气决出胜负吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":200550,"motion":400}]}],"group_43":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_02","textHome":"我是巴麻美，见泷原中学三年级的学生。@是和丘比签订了契约的魔法少女。@还请多多指教。好的，出发吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"id":200550,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_5":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_2005_00_13","textHome":"感觉不错……我的魔力增强了不少。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":200550,"motion":200}]}],"group_6":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"ch